985 ; 195987 ; 195990 ; 195991 ; 195992 ; 195993","2014-04-30T12:00:00.00Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47879/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47879/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/47879/answer",,,,,"26","Business, Innovation and Skills","Business, Innovation and Skills","2014-04-09",,"1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Business, Innovation and Skills, with reference to Growth is Our Business: A Strategy for Professional and Business Services published in July 2013, what progress his Department has made in increasing the number of higher apprenticeships in the professional and business services sector.","false","Biography information for Mr Iain Wright","Hartlepool","Mr Iain Wright","195989"
